hopobject.body: I've got a very weak signal clozapine monitoring medscape Herman Goering (not a friend of democracy it must be admitted) once said…..that whenever anyone mentioned the word “culture” he reached for his revolver….Maybe its not just parades that should be banned in the north but any mention of the word “culture” with the word “my” before it as in …”my culture.” The only alternative is to have the whole population undergo full frontal lobotomies of their brains. That way the whole problem can be surgically removed.
